Credits:
Micro
Di[M]an for his speaker prop model.

Note:
Open ambient_generic properties and go to sound file,change it to the sound file you want to use instead.

You might need to download Di[M]an speaker model and extract it to your css cstrike folder in order to view the speaker model.
Here's the link http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/5211

How to install:
DJTablev1.vmf
Copy and paste it to
C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\{STEAM ACCOUNT}\sourcesdk\bin\orangebox\bin\prefabs

Di[M]an kolonka_dlt
Extract it to your CSS cstrike folder.

Athena.mp3(Optional just in case you're lazy to convert or change the sound file in ambient_generic later).
Copy and paste the disco folder to CSS cstrike\sound folder.
